title: Supply of creamery butter in Canada 2016
summary: The graph shows the Supply of creamery butter Canada in Tonnes Canada during 2016 .
The values are steady for the first three months and peak in April .
The Supply amount generally declines after April except for a significant surge in October and a slight increase in December .
gold: In the following graph is described the monthly supply of creamery butter in tonnes about Canada during 2016 . The minimum value has been registered during the month of January and maximum during July . Furthermore , it 's possible to see how the supply of creamery butter is generally higher during spring and summer .
